This device appears to have been launched around January to Febuary 2002, per [http://www.infohq.com/computer-news-jan02-8-15.htm InfoHQ]. The first appearance of the device on '''Belkin''''s USB hub catalog page is in [http://web.archive.org/web/20020918223109/http://catalog.belkin.com/IWCatSectionView.process?IWAction=Load&Merchant_Id=1&Section_Id=1998&SuperParent=/1889 September 2002] (w/ the last update before that being [http://web.archive.org/web/20020105161401/http://catalog.belkin.com/IWCatSectionView.process?IWAction=Load&Merchant_Id=1&Section_Id=1998&SuperParent=/1889 January 2002]).
